{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hi! This is Bob. He wants to play!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576660/extras/bob.png?t=1520444741\" /><br>Snake Party is a multiplayer game where the player maneuvers a dot that leaves a trail (a.k.a. &quot;Snake&quot;). Based on the concept of classical snake games it enhances the atmosphere, featuring multiple snakes competing against each other. The goal is, to win against the other player's snakes by fooling them with fake strategies and quickly reacting to dangerous situations. You gain points whenever a fellow player hits an obstacle before you do.<br>The controls are fully customizable, just as the number of rounds.<br><br>This is the ultimate party game because it needs <strong>no long explanations</strong>, <strong>no special system requirements</strong>, and can be played by <strong>up to six people</strong> on the same computer! Players choose their own colors, type in their names and the game party is ready to go.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576660/549e62c84e461cc97b5a6ded3f562e1091cbb66d.jpg"},{"name":"Ten deaths","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576660/852c1b198efb4d9369e36461f9b455e54f32db23.jpg"},{"name":"One hundred deaths","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576660/31476fab979ca9ed35ee04645a387de4501ad7f0.jpg"},{"name":"100 Launches","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576660/41e337b2c9873cb2b8aca0970234cf6f2cd949e6.jpg"},{"name":"Long snake","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576660/109d53203631d82d2a1daa764168f74d864c63ce.jpg"},{"name":"You must be crazy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/576660/e29442a97ec5f6fdc93b35472ceb0d38c7c